data.description: Contemporary Comfort in a Greenbelt Community! Discover this modern gem situated at the intersection of Wurzbach Parkway and Blanco Road. Located within a gated neighborhood bordering a tranquil greenbelt, this residence offers a sophisticated lifestyle. Inside, the open layout of the living spaces creates an ideal environment for entertaining and daily living. You'll appreciate the easy-to-maintain tile flooring throughout the downstairs area. The primary bedroom is generously sized and includes an en suite bathroom. In total, there are three bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms, each designed to provide ample space and comfort. With its prime location, modern interior, and natural surroundings, this home offers a harmonious blend of convenience and elegance.
